race.description: Tabtouch Past The Post Payouts Hcp (C1)
race.comment: HEDAWOOD (2) was very good on debut at Belmont, saluting as favourite by 0.2L. The form out of that race is a bit iffy, but Chris Parnham hops in the saddle now and he maps for a similar run in transit today. This looks a suitable race off the debut win and he can go back-to-back. KING'S DRAMA (3) scored in a photo finish last start over 1200m at Belmont and gets the winkers on for the first time today. Steve Parnham takes the ride and with further improvement expected now, he's an attractive commodity. MANJERI (4) was too speedy form the front last time out and it wouldn't surprise to see him do the same back in trip. SESH (5) looks an improver third-up into the campaign.
